text: Greg Cackett (born 14 November 1989) is a British bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:British male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Great Britain Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
